PromotionalEventManagementPlan	create	Create and invoke the promotional event management plan		createPromotionalEventManagementPlan		#desc
PromotionalEventManagementPlan	update	Update details of the promotional event management plan		updatePromotionalEventManagementPlan		#desc
PromotionalEventManagementPlan	request	Request manual intervention in the event plan (e.g. rework participation priorities)		requestPromotionalEventManagementPlan		#desc
PromotionalEventManagementPlan	grant	Obtain a permission grant against the plan (e.g. obtain authority to sponsor an event)		grantPromotionalEventManagementPlan		#desc
PromotionalEventManagementPlan	retrieve	Retrieve details about the promotional event management plan		retrievePromotionalEventManagementPlan		#desc
